      "title": "People marching towards the protest site : Man who paid full fare for train from Kandy to Colombo",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "As massive anti-government protests are taking place in Colombo today, people are marching towards the vacated demonstration grounds.",
        "In this case, two trains have left from Kandy and Galle to Colombo.",
        "It is noteworthy that a trader has paid the entire fare for the train from Kandy to Colombo separately."
